snippet.title: 😲 NO ONE Expects the Acquisition - THE BLOODHALL S16E4
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Bloodhall! Today, we are playing Radha Heir to Keld for one final game, and she already cut off the head of your master. Will she close off her season watching her opponents run home, or will she be defeated by Thada Adel Acquisitor's artifacts, Nicol Bolas the Ravager's planeswalkers, or Omnath Locus of the Roil's elementals? Watch to find out!

Sorry about the weird title, I ran out of room to put the full names of all four commanders.
